      "content": "Advocates for this view stress that fossil fuel reliance is a ticking time bomb, making immediate, powerful decarbonization necessary to avert catastrophe. Nuclear energy, with its near-zero operational emissions, is positioned as a critical tool to provide the baseload power required to meet aggressive net-zero deadlines. While not a perfect solution, its capacity for reliable, high-output, clean energy makes it a pragmatic necessity in the face of climate urgency.",
